<h2>Oakland Energy Incentives</h2>
<p>Oakland residents have access to multiple layers of solar and HVAC incentives that significantly reduce installation costs. The federal Investment Tax Credit (ITC) provides a 30% tax credit for solar installations through 2032, applying to the full cost including equipment, installation, and permits. This credit can be carried forward if it exceeds annual tax liability, making solar accessible to homeowners across all income levels.</p>

